{"title_page": "Leadership approval opinion polling for the next United Kingdom general election", "text_new": "At various dates in the run up to the [[next United Kingdom general election]], various organisations are expected to carry out opinion polling to gauge the opinions that voters hold towards political leaders. Results of such polls are displayed in this article. Most of the polling companies listed are members of the [[British Polling Council]] (BPC) and abide by its disclosure rules.\n\nThe date range for these opinion polls is from the [[2019 United Kingdom general election|previous general election]], held on 12 December 2019, to the present day.\n\n==Leadership approval ratings==\n\n===Boris Johnson===\nThe following polls asked about voters' opinions on [[Boris Johnson]], Leader of the [[Conservative Party (UK)|Conservatives]] and [[Prime Minister of the United Kingdom]].\n\n====2020====\n{| class=\"wikitable collapsible sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:95%;line-height:14px;\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:125px;\" rowspan=\"2\"| Date(s)<br>conducted\n! style=\"width:200px;\" rowspan=\"2\"| Polling organisation/client\n! style=\"width:60px;\" rowspan=\"2\"| Sample size\n! style=\"width:120px;\" rowspan=\"2\"| Question<br>wording\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:80px;\"| Approve\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width: 80px;\"| Disapprove\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:80px;\"| Neither\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:80px;\" rowspan=\"2\"| Don't know\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:20px;\" rowspan=\"2\"| Net approval\n|-\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"background:green;width:60px;\"|\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"background:red;width:60px;\"|\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"background:grey;width:60px;\"|\n|-\n|27 Apr \u2013 1 May\n|[https://www.opinium.co.uk/public-opinion-on-coronavirus-27th-april/ Opinium]\n|2,000\n|Approve/Disapprove\n|style=\"background:#C1F0C1\"| '''51%'''\n|31%\n|{{N/A}}\n|18%\n|style=\"background:gre