 6-9 December asked voters to state whether they like or dislike Drakeford on a scale of 0-10.\n{| class=\"wikitable collapsible sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:95%;line-height:14px;\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:125px;\" | Date(s)<br>conducted\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:200px;\" | Polling organisation/client\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:60px;\" | Sample size\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:120px;\" | Question<br>wording\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:80px;\" | Approve\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width: 80px;\" | Disapprove\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:80px;\" | Neither\n! rowspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:80px;\" | Don't know\n! rowspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:20px;\" | Net approval\n|-\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"background:green;width:60px;\" |\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"background:red;width:60px;\" |\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"background:grey;width:60px;\" |\n|-\n|6\u20139 Dec\n|[http://blogs.cardiff.ac.uk/electionsinwales/wp-content/uploads/sites/100/2019/12/December-2019.pdf YouGov]\n|1,020\n|Like/Dislike\n|11%\n| style=\"background:#FFD2D2\" |'''32%'''\n|8%\n|48%\n| style=\"background:red;color:white;\" |'''\u221221%'''\n|}\n\n==Approval ratings for former party leaders==\n\n===Jeremy Corbyn===\nThe following polls asked about voters' opinions on [[Jeremy Corbyn]], the former Leader of the [[Labour Party (UK)|Labour Party]].\n\n====2020====\n{| class=\"wikitable collapsible sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:95%;line-height:14px;\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:125px;\" rowspan=\"2\"| Date(s)<br>conducted\n! style=\"width:200px;\" rowspan=\"2\"| Polling organisation/client\n! style=\"width:60px;\" rowspan=\"2\"| Sample size\n! style=\"width:120px;\" rowspan=\"2\"| Question<br>wording\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:80px;\"| Approve\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width: 80px;\"| Disapprove\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:80px;\"| Neither\n! class=\"unso